  21 Feb 2007; Piotr Jaroszyński <peper@gentoo.org> ChangeLog:
  Transition to Manifest2.

  05 Jan 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rskkserv-2.95.3.ebuild,
  rskkserv-2.95.3-r1.ebuild, rskkserv-2.95.4.ebuild:
  Convert to use elog.

  14 Oct 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> rskkserv-2.95.3.ebuild,
  rskkserv-2.95.3-r1.ebuild, rskkserv-2.95.4.ebuild:
  Use make DESTDIR install instead of einstall, fixes sandbox violation
  reported in bug #151279 by Patrick Lauer.

  03 Aug 2005; Bryan Østergaard <kloeri@gentoo.org>
  rskkserv-2.95.3-r1.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha.

